1
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:30,480
Dad

2
00:01:31,079 --> 00:01:33,000
I'll be back once I finalize the supply chain in Shenzhen

3
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,400
Take care of yourself

4
00:01:34,959 --> 00:01:35,840
Don't worry

5
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:38,840
Sister Dolma

6
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:42,359
From now on, this old man

7
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,359
I'm leaving him in your hands

8
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,319
This is the Chinese jewelry I picked out

9
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,200
It's really beautiful

10
00:01:49,599 --> 00:01:50,079
It's a gift for you

11
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:51,879
I can't accept this

12
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:52,840
This is way too valuable

13
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:54,680
Don't be so polite

14
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,799
Soon I might not be calling you "sister" anymore

15
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,000
Right?

16
00:01:58,239 --> 00:01:58,680
Old man

17
00:01:58,760 --> 00:01:59,640
What are you talking about?

18
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:04,920
The car's here

19
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:07,519
Thanks for everything

20
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:08,960
Stay safe

21
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,000
I'm off

22
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,039
Bye, bye

23
00:02:13,639 --> 00:02:14,479
I'm leaving, old man

24
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,759
Be safe

25
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:18,400
Come back soon, I'm off

26
00:02:35,199 --> 00:02:35,719
Haoran

27
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,199
Your village posting is over

28
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,120
It's time to head back

29
00:02:40,479 --> 00:02:40,960
Party Secretary

30
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:42,120
Say no more

31
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:45,000
The villagers will remember these past two years

32
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:46,560
This is your home too

33
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:47,919
Come back and visit often

34
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:48,800
Alright

35
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,039
Cadre Haoran

36
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,439
Do a good job when you get back

37
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:52,960
Don't embarrass our village

38
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,319
Can't you speak more nicely?

39
00:02:57,759 --> 00:02:58,199
Alright

40
00:02:58,199 --> 00:02:59,000
Thank you, everyone

41
00:02:59,240 --> 00:02:59,879
Thank you, thank you

42
00:03:15,639 --> 00:03:16,280
Qianqian

43
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,759
Take care of yourself

44
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:23,800
I will

45
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:27,719
I'm off

46
00:03:36,879 --> 00:03:37,479
Take care

47
00:03:39,159 --> 00:03:40,080
Go on, hurry

48
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,360
Thank you, everyone

49
00:03:44,719 --> 00:03:45,319
I'm leaving now

50
00:03:45,599 --> 00:03:46,439
Come back to visit often

51
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:47,560
Get in the car

52
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:51,280
Going to miss him?

53
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,520
Not at all

54
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,319
Not at all

55
00:03:57,719 --> 00:03:59,520
Then whose eyes are red?

56
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,439
The wind is strong, can't you feel it?

57
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:05,879
I'm leaving now, Qianqian

58
00:04:33,279 --> 00:04:34,000
Zhaxi

59
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:35,879
Where are you taking me?

60
00:04:42,319 --> 00:04:43,040
Zhaxi

61
00:04:43,439 --> 00:04:44,959
Where exactly are you taking me?

62
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:57,639
Why did you bring me here?

63
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:00,480
Meiduo

64
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:03,439
Look at these mountains

65
00:05:04,639 --> 00:05:05,360
these trees

66
00:05:06,959 --> 00:05:07,839
these flowers

67
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:09,959
I never used to understand

68
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:12,560
I didn't understand you

69
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:14,920
why, over a single blade of grass

70
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,600
you'd laugh, cry

71
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:18,720
get angry

72
00:05:19,199 --> 00:05:20,160
even risk your life

73
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:22,319
But then I understood

74
00:05:23,839 --> 00:05:24,959
Animals cry out when hurt

75
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,040
People cry when hungry

76
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,079
But these plants

77
00:05:30,759 --> 00:05:32,480
when they're pulled up by the roots

78
00:05:33,839 --> 00:05:35,560
they can't make a single sound

79
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:38,279
You work so hard to record them

80
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,800
just so that one day

81
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,040
they'll be remembered, right?

82
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,600
You once told me

83
00:05:50,199 --> 00:05:51,720
you planted more than one lingzhi mushroom

84
00:05:52,519 --> 00:05:53,439
Whenever I had time

85
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:55,319
I'd go searching in the mountains

86
00:05:56,879 --> 00:05:58,279
But I still couldn't find any

87
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,240
This

88
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,680
I learned to weave it from Sister Zhuoma

89
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,720
I worked on it for three months

90
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,560
ruined seven or eight of them

91
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,000
Only this one came out decent

92
00:06:20,879 --> 00:06:21,800
I know

93
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:24,360
this can't replace your seed source

94
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,720
But I promise you

95
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:28,759
one day

96
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,160
we'll definitely find it

97
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,040
Then hurry up and put it on me

98
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:55,160
There you go

99
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:00,360
Does it look good?

100
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:01,879
It looks great

101
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:09,839
What else?

102
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,720
That's it

103
00:07:18,319 --> 00:07:18,959
Hand it over, quick

104
00:07:38,079 --> 00:07:38,639
Meiduo

105
00:07:41,279 --> 00:07:42,800
I don't really get all that

106
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,480
research, data, and all that stuff

107
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:47,959
A lot of what you write

108
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,439
I can't understand

109
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:52,360
But

110
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,600
these mountains

111
00:07:54,399 --> 00:07:54,959
I understand them

112
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:58,519
Every path in this forest

113
00:07:58,519 --> 00:07:59,720
every tree

114
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,439
I know them all

115
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,079
From now on

116
00:08:04,519 --> 00:08:05,959
if you want to go into the mountains

117
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,800
I'll carry you there

118
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:12,000
If you want to plant something

119
00:08:13,519 --> 00:08:14,560
I'll dig the soil for you

120
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:18,240
If you want

121
00:08:19,839 --> 00:08:20,920
to stay here forever

122
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:23,920
I'll stay here with you

123
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:29,759
Will you

124
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:31,800
say yes?

125
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,679
I meant for you to pay me back

126
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:47,960
Eighteen thousand

127
00:08:48,519 --> 00:08:49,799
How long are you gonna owe me?

128
00:08:50,759 --> 00:08:51,159
I'll

129
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,480
owe you for a year

130
00:09:00,759 --> 00:09:01,440
A year?

131
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,440
Then two years

132
00:09:03,559 --> 00:09:04,320
Two years?

133
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,039
Then make it

134
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:05,960
this many years

135
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:06,799
No

136
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:07,440
Not enough, not enough

137
00:09:07,559 --> 00:09:09,159
It's gotta be forty, sixty years

138
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:11,360
Eighty years, a hundred years

139
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,080
Meiduo

140
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:15,960
I'll owe you for a lifetime
